Save image : bpy.ops.image.save()
Save image as : bpy.ops.image.save_as()
Render image : bpy.ops.render.render()
Add camera : bpy.ops.object.camera_add()

Activate Zbuffer : ImageFormatSettings.use_zbuffer
Specify output : ImageFormatSettings.file_format
Demander Z au rendering : SceneRenderLayer.use_pass_z
